          "debateRelevance": "Useful when debating whether places need a clear practical role in order to deserve attention, beauty, and emotional value.",
          "counterargument": "People may be drawn to liminal spaces for discomfort, nostalgia, or cultural fashion as much as for anything that resembles Kantian beauty.",
