          "debateRelevance": "Useful when debating whether emotional experience in waiting spaces comes mainly from design or mainly from the stressful event people are anticipating.",
          "counterargument": "Design matters, but it may not outweigh the deeper anxiety caused by what people are waiting for in the first place.",
