          "debateRelevance": "Useful when debating whether ambient sound can genuinely improve liminal spaces or whether it simply fills silence without solving the deeper experience of waiting.",
          "counterargument": "Ambient music may support atmosphere, but it is not inherently tied to liminal spaces and may function just as well as a broader aesthetic choice.",
