          "guidingSection": "Where the Sidewalk Starts",
          "rawOfficialText": "Dubai barely has them; in New York they’re bustling with people and halal food stands. Research the history of the sidewalk - that liminal gap between street and building that serves as a gathering place for some and a bike path for others. Where did they first emerge - and when were the first modern sidewalks built? How different are they from place to place?",
