          "title": "Turning Parking Into Public Space",
          "guidingSection": "Where the Sidewalk Starts",
          "rawOfficialText": "Landscape architects RIOS transformed one set of downtown parking lots into a new community gathering place, then discuss with your team: are there places in your own city that should be converted in a similar way?",
