          "debateRelevance": "Useful when debating whether futuristic roads truly improve mobility or simply shift cost, repair, surveillance, and environmental burdens elsewhere.",
          "counterargument": "Some smart-road ideas may stay niche because they are too expensive, fragile, complex, or difficult to maintain outside special settings.",
